In large saucepan melt butter over low heat. Add marshmallows and stir until completely melted. Remove from heat. Add KELLOGG'S RICE KRISPIES cereal. Stir until well coated. Cool slightly. Using buttered hands shape mixture into 8 snakes. Place on wax-paper-lined baking sheet. Cool. Decorate with KELLOGG'S APPLE JACKS cereal, KELLOGG'S FROOT LOOPS cereal, frosting, berries and/or candies as snake eyes and markings. Best if served the same day.